  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with multiple sclerosis

          -  Expanded Disability Status Scale score &lt; or = 5

          -  Fatigue (Modified Fatigue Impact Scale &gt; 45), with a disease duration &gt; 3 months

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Depression

          -  Cognitive disorders

          -  EDSS &gt; 5

          -  Epilepsia

          -  Obesity

          -  Drug inducing sleep disorders
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
